# Installation

Follow these steps to get running.

{% callout type="warning" title="Prerequisites" %}
You need Node.js 20.9 or newer.
{% /callout %}

```bash
npm install
npm run dev
```

This deeply nested page lives at `guides/getting-started/install`, which maps to
the folder structure on disk and the URL `/docs/guides/getting-started/install`.
